      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V and UHMWPE material properties are drawn from the 2025 Q3 lot-specific characterization dataset (dataVintage 2025-09-30). Geometric inputs (screw shank diameter, rod diameter, block dimensions) are from CMM measurements of production components used in bench testing. Input uncertainty (±2% on elastic modulus, ±3% on yield strength) has been propagated via Monte Carlo sampling to the QoI uncertainty budget. Re-validation against the revised geometry tolerance band introduced in the February 2026 model revision is planned for Q2 2026. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
