      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs from two production-representative lots were tested. Full traceability (lot number, serial number, dimensional inspection report) documented for each construct. CMM inspection confirms all components within drawing tolerances. Sample size exceeds the minimum N=10 threshold. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
