      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA model inputs (geometry, material properties, boundary conditions) are demonstrably equivalent to the physical test configuration. Any deviations are quantified and their effect on QoIs bounded.",
      "rationale": "FEA geometry was derived from the same CMM measurements used to characterize the bench-tested constructs. Potting depth and block spacing in the model match the physical fixture to within 0.5 mm. Boundary conditions (fixed base, vertical displacement ramp at load point) replicate the test machine configuration. No unquantified deviations identified. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
